### Display Content Based on Dynamic Route Params

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/03-api-reference/03-file-conventions/page.mdx

Access dynamic route segment parameters using the params prop in async page components. The params prop is now a Promise that must be awaited to retrieve the actual parameter values from the URL.

```typescript
